OL,6,FWomen in south-western face a 70-plus
OL,7,Fmile journey whilst in labour, leaving
OL,8,Fsome giving birth in lay-bys, an ITV
OL,9,FNews investigation has found.
OL,11,FEvidence gathered was presented to the
OL,12,Fn Edinburgh, which described it as a
OL,13,F"concern."
OL,15,FOne woman, Debbie Kelly, described how
OL,16,Fshe had her sixth child in 2021 "in a
OL,17,Flay-by on the Gatehouse bypass" after
OL,18,Fnot getting to the main hospital in
OL,19,FDumfries, 50 miles away from her home,
OL,20,Fin time.
