OL,6,F"It was scary, it was horrible," she
OL,7,Fsaid.
OL,9,FAfter going into labour Ms Kelly
OL,10,Ftravelled to but was told to return
OL,11,Fhome, despite her objections, after
OL,12,Fher pregnancy progressed slowly. When
OL,13,Fher contractions began several hours
OL,14,Flater, she was taken back up the road
