OL,6,FWigtownshire sits in the south-west of
OL,7,F, with its largest town, Stranraer,
OL,8,Falong the coast over seventy miles
OL,9,Faway from .
OL,11,FUntil 2018, women with low-risk
OL,12,Fpregnancies could give birth at a
OL,13,Fmaternity unit in the town. It was
OL,14,Fmothballed due to low staff numbers,
OL,15,Fand for the last six years women have
OL,16,Fhad to travel to the to give birth.
OL,18,FThe NHS offers home births in the
OL,19,Fregion, although ITV News didn't speak
OL,20,Fto any women who had been offered one.
