OL,6,FAn independent review into maternity
OL,7,Fservice provision in was published in
OL,8,FJune 2023.
OL,10,FIt then presented two options to the
OL,11,FNHS, which then launched a
OL,12,Fconsultation with local people. One of
OL,13,Fthe options presented was that the
OL,14,Funit should remain closed, with only
OL,15,Fsome, low-risk home births to take
OL,16,Fplace in Wigtownshire. The other would
OL,17,Freturn births to the unit in Stranraer.
OL,19,FAccording to , less than a quarter of
OL,20,Fall births in Wigtownshire are classed
OL,21,Fas low-risk.
