OL,6,FThe consultation concluded in
OL,7,FFebruary, with a decision expected
OL,8,Flater in 2024.
OL,10,FCampaigners have been calling for the
OL,11,Freturn of the maternity unit since its
OL,12,Fclosure. Clare Fleming, who was told
OL,13,Fshe'd lost her baby in Stranraer and
OL,14,Fthen had to drive over 70 miles to
OL,15,FDumfries to deliver it, said it was
OL,16,Ffor "women to choose where to give
OL,17,Fbirth, not for the NHS to tell us."
